<paragraph id="8BCDCB49A674FF99FF33FF0D4254FF44" blockId="5.[151,1437,151,645]" box="[199,1038,151,176]" pageId="5" pageNumber="448">Legs. Apical tarsomere with arolium, claws without tooth on inner margin.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCDCB49A674FF99FF33FF2847FAFEE8" blockId="5.[151,1437,151,645]" pageId="5" pageNumber="448">Metasoma. Petiole slightly coriaceous, weakly shiny, with several fine punctures. Metasomal segment smooth and shiny, with several tiny punctures. Relative length of petiole: hindtarsomere I: II: III = 28: 41: 20: 15. Genitalia as figs 11, 12.</paragraph>
